{
  "texts": [
    "Some interviewees, especially those in leadership positions, may have framed their company's approach to AI and environmental sustainability in a more favorable light, consciously or unconsciously aligning their answers with perceived best practices.",
    "This concurs with research indicating that professionals often tailor their responses to align with expected corporate narratives [51].",
    "Future studies could mitigate this limitation by incorporating observational data or case studies alongside self-reported interviews.",
    "Nonetheless, the small number of applied Green AI practices was explicitly recognized by the participants, suggesting that they answered fairly truthfully.",
    "As the power of AI continues to grow, it is important to further study how to profit from this technology without harming the environment and society."
  ]
}